{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-412-gnomon-numbering","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 412: Brojevi za gnomon","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Za celobrojke $m$, $n$ ($0 ≤ n &#x3C; m$), neka je $L(m, n)$ mreža od $m \\times m$ iz koje je uklonjena gornjo-desna mreža od $n \\times n$.</p>\n<p>Na primer, $L(5, 3)$ izgleda ovako:</p>\n<img alt=\"5x5 grid, with removed 3x3 grid from the top-right\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/gnomon-numbering-1.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Želimo dodeliti svakoj ćeliji $L(m, n)$ uzastopne brojeve 1, 2, 3, ... na način da je broj u svakoj ćeliji manji od broja koji je ispod nje i sa njene leve strane.</p>\n<p>Na primer, ovo su dva validna broja za $L(5, 3)$:</p>\n<img alt=\"two valid numberings of L(5, 3)\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/gnomon-numbering-2.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Neka je $LC(m, n)$ broj validnih brojeva za $L(m, n)$. Može se dokazati da je $LC(3, 0) = 42$, $LC(5, 3) = 250\\,250$, $LC(6, 3) = 406\\,029\\,023\\,400$ i $LC(10, 5)\\bmod 76\\,543\\,217 = 61\\,251\\,715$.</p>\n<p>Izračunaj $LC(10\\,000, 5\\,000)\\bmod 76\\,543\\,217$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f5081000cf542c51001a","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302081,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-412-gnomon-numbering"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function gnomonNumbering() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ngnomonNumbering();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>gnomonNumbering()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>38788800</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(gnomonNumbering(), 38788800);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-401-to-480","dashedName":"problem-412-gnomon-numbering","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-413-one-child-numbers","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-411-uphill-paths","id":"5900f5081000cf542c51001a","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-412-gnomon-numbering"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}